dcterms:description: A dataset containing aggregated solar PV power generation data from 12 PV plants in New South Wales, Australia, with a total capacity of 600 MW, sampled at 30-minute intervals during daytime hours.
dcterms:title: NSW Solar Power Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing aggregated solar PV power generation data from 19 PV plants in Queensland, Australia, with a total capacity of 1106 MW, sampled at 30-minute intervals during daytime hours.
dcterms:title: QLD Solar Power Dataset
